news.title: Insomniacs powers India’s top realty players with agentic Convo AI to redefine sales, channel partner engagement and post sales
news.para: Indian real estate is embracing digital maturity with Insomniacs' AI tools. Convo AI and TrustED AI are transforming developer engagement, from marketing to post-sales. These systems handle queries, analyze interactions, and personalize communication in multiple Indian languages. Developers are seeing improved conversions and efficiency without extra staff. This intelligent automation is powering the future of property sales.

news.title: Mountain shadows resorts: A model of eco-sensitive and disaster-resilient architecture in Wayanad
news.para: Mountain Shadows Resort in Wayanad exemplifies eco-sensitive and disaster-resilient design, blending seamlessly with its lake island setting through stilted structures and ecological restoration. Prakriti Aawaas in Kochi revolutionizes eco-friendly living, merging architecture with nature on a 2-acre site, fostering community and ecological well-being through sustainable design and traditional inspiration.

news.title: Construction noises rob Nagpur residents of peace & sleep
news.para: Nagpur residents are facing unbearable noise pollution due to relentless construction activity, with work often extending from 6 am to 11 pm. Builders' race to meet deadlines disregards the well-being of citizens, leading to sleep deprivation and increased family tension. Despite numerous complaints, civic authorities have failed to implement effective regulations for construction timings and noise levels.
